    <%- include('_header.ejs') %>
    <main class="writingediting">
      <h1>Writing & Editing Freelancing</h1>
      <p>
        The world of freelance writing and editing offers a diverse range of
        opportunities for those with strong communication and creative skills.
        From crafting compelling content to ensuring flawless grammar and
        clarity, freelance writers and editors play a crucial role in various
        industries.
      </p>
      <h2>Finding Work</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Freelance platforms: Upwork, Fiverr, Freelancer.com</li>
        <li>Niche job boards: ProBlogger, Problogger Jobs, The Write Life</li>
        <li>Direct outreach: Contact businesses and publications directly</li>
      </ul>
      <h2>Success Tips</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          Build a strong portfolio showcasing your writing and editing skills.
        </li>
        <li>
          Craft compelling proposals that highlight your expertise and value
          proposition.
        </li>
        <li>
          Maintain excellent communication with clients and deliver projects on
          time.
        </li>
        <li>
          Develop effective time management skills to handle multiple projects.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <h2>Tools & Resources</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Grammarly: Online grammar checker and writing assistant</li>
        <li>Copyscape: Plagiarism detection tool</li>
        <li>Trello: Project management software</li>
        <li>
          The Freelance Writer's Guide: Online resource with freelance writing
          tips
        </li>
        <li>
          The Editing Company: Online resource for editors with best practices
        </li>
      </ul>
    </main>
